<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 &quot;A theimi vialte ra u,&quot; ti-in au tuah, Vanrang kulh chung ah hi
 thawngtha kha an duh; Mi umnak vialte ah lawmhnak bia thanh u, Rat duhmi
 vialte ra u.

[C1]
   Rat duhmi zeihmanh, Rat duhmi zeihmanh; Tlang le hor khua zakip ah
   thawngtha va thanh, A kan dawt kan Pa nih misual a auh hna, &quot;Rat duhmi
   vialte ra u.&quot;

[V2]
 Rat duhmi vialte nih ngang len hna hlah seh, Vancung innka a hung atu
 an lut kho; Lu-nunnak lam ngai cu Jesuh a si ko, Rat duhmi vialte ra u.

[C2]
   Rat duhmi zeihmanh, Rat duhmi zeihmanh; Tlang le hor khua zakip ah
   thawngtha va thanh, A kan dawt kan Pa nih misual a auh hna, &quot;Rat duhmi
   vialte ra u.&quot;

[V3]
 Rat duhmi vialte an bia-kamnak a hmun, Rat duhmi vialte a zungzal in
 an nung; Rat duhmi vialte lu-nunnak kha a um, Rat duhmi vialte ra u.

[C3]
   Rat duhmi zeihmanh, Rat duhmi zeihmanh; Tlang le hor khua zakip ah
   thawngtha va thanh, A kan dawt kan Pa nih misual a auh hna, &quot;Rat duhmi
   vialte ra u.&quot;</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<title>RAT DUHMI VIALTE CH238</title>
<hymn_number>238</hymn_number>
</song>